name: Willow Prototype
description:
D E S C R I P T I O N :

Willow Oregon, June ██ 198█ 

You woke up                                                                                                                                                                    

In a foggy area                                                                                                                                                               

all you remember is a job,

a coin,

and a car...

but you also remember a town up the road called 'Willow'

==Dev Note==

This is a model/environment test for my game "Willow". The early beta release date is unknown, If you want to volunteer as a coder just say you want to volunteer and I will contact you VIA email or Skype (Discord is also an option). There are some unfinished and buggy models on here and I know it so don't point that out, just give me suggestions on how I can make the game better in the future!

This is a survival game.

The Game is made on Unity 5 personal edition

I hope you like this test map :P
